<h2>What is really it about?</h2>

<div class="hero-unit">
	<p>
		<strong>Altarion : Universal Supremacy</strong> aims to be the best real time universal wide strategy game ever produced.
		<br>
		<br>
		
		It's 4242, the hyperspace system suddenly ends existing, leaving thousands of colonies on their own. Become one of their leaders, build a full civilisation from the ashes of the old Empire, and survive the race for domination.
		<br>
		<br>
		
		<strong>Altarion : Universal Supremacy</strong> is being developped as a project for the video game course, given for the <a href="http://mti.epita.fr">MTI</a> specialisation at <a href="http://www.epita.fr">EPITA</a>
	</p>
</div>